// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-1849 — Mass File Rename (qilin)
// Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 784ac397-0ec9-53fa-9000-cc5899ca888e

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
